        <h2>
            写给年轻人的哲学史的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 1 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7481652">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7481652/" class="title-link">哲学让我们找到自己、幸福与快乐</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7481652"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/117800068/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u117800068-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/117800068/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">就这样活着吧</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-05-25"
      class="main-meta">2015-05-25 11:51:17</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7481652_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这是一本哲学普及读物。是一本简要的关于哲学发展史的书籍，也更像一本查询各时期重要的哲学家及其思想与著作的工具书。对于这样一本书，要写读书心得还真的比较困难。我唯一的心得是通过这本书让我对哲学有了一个很粗浅的认识，包括其发展、思想流派、各流派哲学家与其著作等...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7481652_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7481652_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










